sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner as Trucking Owner
    participant Web as Web App
    participant Backend as Backend App
    participant Storage as File Storage
    participant PDF as PDF Processor
    participant DB as Database

    Owner->>Web: Upload load PDF
    Web->>Backend: POST /loads/documents/upload

    Backend->>Backend: Validate owner authentication and role

    Backend->>Storage: Upload PDF file
    Storage-->>Backend: Return file_url

    Backend->>DB: Insert document with PROCESSING status
    DB-->>Backend: Return document_id

    Backend->>PDF: Process load document using file_url
    PDF-->>Backend: Return extracted load data

    Backend->>Backend: Validate extracted fields

    Backend->>DB: Update document with extracted_data and PENDING_OWNER_REVIEW
    DB-->>Backend: Document updated

    Backend-->>Web: Return extracted data for review
    Web-->>Owner: Show extracted data with editable fields

    Owner->>Web: Review/edit extracted fields and click Approve
    Web->>Backend: POST /loads/documents/{documentId}/approve

    Backend->>Backend: Validate owner-approved load data

    Backend->>DB: Insert load using approved data
    DB-->>Backend: Return load_id

    Backend->>DB: Update document with load_id and APPROVED status
    DB-->>Backend: Document updated

    Backend-->>Web: Return load created successfully
    Web-->>Owner: Show created load